@startuml
title Assets - Level 1

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0

class "Image" as Image
class "Sprite sheet" as SpriteSheet
class "Font" as Font
class "Mesh" as Mesh
class "Widget" as Widget
class "Drawing command" as DrawingCommand

Widget --> DrawingCommand : creates
DrawingCommand --> Image : can use
DrawingCommand --> SpriteSheet : can use
DrawingCommand --> Font : can use
DrawingCommand --> Mesh : can use

note bottom
Assets are reusable data. Widgets combine assets
with drawing commands to display something.
end note

@enduml
